channel.title: Cache Help
channel.description: Hello everyone I use PwnScape client and source. Lately I've worked on my game alot and got tired of the floating helmets. I used Aeolians tutorial and i got snow models for metal fences. There was a solution there but it didn't work. I now use his new replaced textures cache. Personally I don't like it. And I can't find a cache that can support my Vesta Long & spear, d bow, statius warhammer etc. If anyone could help. Please don't come with the search bar. I have billions and billions of times. Downloading client after client and trying to use the cache. Or if anybody has a cache that is undamaged and has normal textures if they could give me a link or soemthing. Or even a way to change back the textures using Tom's Cache Suite. Idk how to change floors and etc. Thanks
